songs.title: Million Dollars
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
And this beat by ChaseTheMoney, he gon’ sell some dope with me

[Hook]
I just wanna fuck your bitch on a million dollars, aye
Stackin’ up the guap until I see a million dollars, aye
It’s a good girl, oh yeah, it’s a bomb bae
I had took the lean and I mixed it with some Bombay
Old school’s clean, I was showin’ that bitch off
Tappin’ on the gas, I was snatchin’ in it often
Old bitch was trippin’, I had told that bitch get lost
Waitin’ on my shipment, I don’t think that shit took off yet

Bitch was suckin’ on my dick so good, I felt her tonsils
I just paid the club to wipe the coupe for fifty dollars
I just got this new hoe number, but I didn’t call her
